texts.text: >On a night where the moon's thin crescent casts a feint light...
>Somewhere within a dark and sleepy orphanage,
>a girl sits and prays...
God, are you there? It's me... The director got mad at me again...
Every day, they keep saying, "You're a bag girl, Elisa." Sometimes, they beat me too.
I don't even know what I'm doing wrong...

*Sob*
Mommy... Daddy...
>The girl's shoulders shutter as she tries to hold back her tears...
*Groan*
>She hears a noise and turns her head to see.
*Groan*
Huh...? Did someone just say something...?
>She has trouble finding the source of the noise.
>But the strange sound continues to echo in the girl's ears...

Wake...
Awaken...
God, is that you?!
Huh?! What did you just say to me?!
Awaken...
Awaken God...
Huh...?
God...?
Devil Download!
*Screech*
*Groan*
Seriously, will you just give up already?!
*Roar*
*Groan*
Phew. We've cleared out quite a few demons from this place.
Ugh... All we've been doing these past few days is fighting these things.
On top of that, I haven't been able to get any shifts in at work...
Agreed. I haven't had any time to enjoy a good cup of coffee either.

Hm? Oh.
Hey, Vince.
Aight, y'all, let's keep that talk to a minimum.
We still don't know what's causin' all this, but we do know that Tokyo's probably in danger.
Ah. Hello, Megakin.
Your teams were working together just now?
Yup!
Newbie and I, plus Vince and Honey, were trackin' down those demons.
Yeah, we met up with Newbie and beat the snot out of them!
That was rough.
That was fun.
In that case, well done.
Nice work, [sys user_name].

Yo, don't forget about Rika & Shiang Sun
and Shionyan & Meat Balloon.
Just got updates from them too.
Really?!
So that means we can take a quick break, right...?
You got it!
Still got no idea where these things are gonna hit next so...
Yo, we gotta take breaks whenever we can.
Yay! I'm totally beat after running around all this time...!
Me too!
Hey, partner, don't forget who has to carry you around.

Hm?
Oh, I guess you're right.

*Sigh*
Honey's cuteness just makes everything so much better...
But I still don't understand.
Why are so many stray demons running around here now?
Yo, about that...
It all started three days ago with just one sighting.
The first ones weren't even all that strong, you know?
But more and more just keep showin' up.
Quite a few at once too...
Now, we have to break into teams in order to handle them all.
Yeah, and Seiran's usually here to help us whenever this stuff happens.
By telling us, "I sense a disturbance in the Dragon Stream."
However, she said it wasn't that.
Hmm... This is a tough one.
Yeah, if only we knew what's causing all this.
At this rate, we won't get anywhere. What do you think, boss?
Yo, I get how you feel.
We ain't gonna last much longer if we all have to keep fightin' like this.
Plus, we have Shiang Sun lookin' for leads online.
And Seiran's doin' eveyrthin' she can to make sure it's not the Dragon Stream.
We just gotta grin and bear it until we figure somethin' out.
Yeah, I'd hate to see my brother and sister get sucked into all this.
I'll keep going.
Wait... Huh?
Is something the matter, Ririn?
Yeah, look! Over there!
That cute, little girl just keeps staring at us♪
>You all look to see and the girl scurries behind a tree!
>Then, she jumps out and starts running towards all of you!
E-Excuse me!
Yes, sweetie♪ Is something wrong?
Can we help you?

I... Uh...!
I'm Elisa!
Um...
What was that thing I saw just now?!
Huh?
You were fighting this weird thing that I'd never seen before!
It's gone now, but it was all see-through and...
Yo, hold up. Can this kid...?
She can see demons and Decoherence Fields...
That was my first time seeing anything like that...
So, if you know what's going on, please tell me.
Tell me how to wake God up...!
